Package: tidylearn
Title: Tidy Supervised Learning Tools
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
  person(given = "Cesaire",
         family = "Tobias",
         role = c("aut", "cre"),
         email = "cesaire@sheetsolved.com")
Description: A comprehensive toolkit for supervised machine learning that follows tidyverse principles.
  This package provides consistent interfaces for model training, evaluation, and visualization across various
  supervised learning algorithms including regression, classification, tree-based methods, SVM, neural networks,
  and deep learning approaches. It emphasizes intuitive syntax, pipeline-friendly operations, and informative visualizations.
